org.openflow.protocol.table

Class OFTableResource

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openflow.protocol.table.OFTableResource

  • public class OFTableResource
extends java.lang.Object
    OFTableResource describes the table resource information of one table type. It is a part of OFFlowTableResource

    OFTableResource
    {
    int32 deviceID;
    int8 tableType;
    int8 tableNum; //how many tables of this kind of table type could be
    int16 keyLength;

    int32 totalSize; //how many total entries of this kind of table type could be
    int32 reserve;
    } //sizeof() = 16

    Author:
    Song Jian (jack.songjian@huawei.com), Huawei Technologies Co., Ltd.
